O Vale Onde O Tempo Parou

description: The Amazons are under new leadership and his name is Achilles. The God of War may be gone, but his plans to destroy Wonder Woman and the Amazons are still very much alive. The opposition gains a much needed boost when Donna Troy arrives to confront her sister. In this issue we see the coronation of the new Queen, Alkyone, and that is only the beginning.
name: Warkiller, Part 2 of 4: Of Two Minds

description: “Starstalker” Part 2 finds Nova and his fledgling Corps pitted against a threat from another dimension, forced to team up with the galaxy’s deadliest bounty hunter, and coping with a blast from the past!
name: Krushed

description: Comic strip: Darkness Falling, the first prelude to the forthcoming The Mark of Mandragora. The Doctor does not appear in the main comic strip, but does in the Comic Assassins' strip reviewing Curse of Fenric, in the Brief Encounters text story, and in a sample of a proposed Doctor Who newspaper strip, which also features his companion Ace and the Daleks.
Part 1 of The Mark of Mandragora, a sequel to the television story The Masque of Mandragora.
Includes the fourth and final installment of The Mark of Mandragora, plus illustrated prose story A Victorian Interlude.

In the comic strip, Party Animals, the seventh Doctor and his companion, Ace, travel to Maruthea to celebrate Bonjaxx's birthday. Many of his old friends and foes are present including Death's Head and Abslom Daak and a future incarnation of the himself.
name: Party Animals
